<%last_message_sent_time = @user.last_message_sent_time %>
Hi <%= @user.handle %>,
<%= Message.since(Time.now - 1.week).count %>  messages have been exchanged in the last week.
<%if last_message_sent_time %>
<%= Message.since(@user.last_message_sent_time).count %> since your last message <%= time_ago_in_words(@user.last_message_sent_time) %> ago.
<% else %>
You haven't sent any messages yet! Why not try now?
<% end %>
Thanks for reading and have a great day!
